  <summary date="2021-06-28T14:53:11Z" status="Introduced in House">Kids Eat Local Act 

This bill modifies Department of Agriculture requirements for the national school food programs relating to the purchases of locally produced food.

The bill allows institutions participating in the school food programs to use locally grown, locally raised, or locally caught as a product specification in food procurement requests.</summary>
